web|url=https://yle.fi/uutiset/osasto/news/woman_in_helsinki_tests_positive_for_novel_coronavirus/11229433|title=Woman in Helsinki tests positive for novel coronavirus|website=Yle Uutiset|access-date=26 February 2020}}</ref>\nOn 28 February, a Finnish woman who had travelled to Northern Italy tested positive at the Helsinki and Uusimaa Hospital District and was placed in home isolation.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://yle.fi/uutiset/osasto/news/new_coronavirus_infection_confirmed_in_helsinki/11234516|title=New coronavirus infection confirmed in Helsinki|website=Yle Uutiset|access-date=1 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://yle.fi/uutiset/osasto/news/new_coronavirus_infection_confirmed_in_helsinki/11234516|title=New coronavirus infection confirmed in Helsinki|website=Yle Uutiset|access-date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n'''France''' \u2013\nOn 25 February, France confirmed that a 64-year-old man from [[La Balme-de-Sillingy]] who had returned from a trip to Lombardy on 15 February tested positive and was treated at Centre Hospitalier Annecy-Genevois, [[\u00c9pagny-Metz-Tessy]].<ref name=\"Repubblica_25Feb_Europe\"/><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-health-france-idUSKBN20J2CG|title=France reports two new coronavirus infections, one returning from Italy|date=25 February 2020|agency=Reuters|access-date=26 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ladepeche.fr/2020/02/25/direct-coronavirus-loms-evoque-un-risque-de-pandemie-pour-la-premiere-fois,8754380.php|title=DIRECT. Coronavirus : deux nouveaux cas identifi\u00e9s en France|website=ladepeche.fr|language=fr|access-date=27 February 2020}}</ref> His wife also tested positive and was admitted to the same hospital.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ledauphine.com/faits-divers-justice/2020/02/26/haute-savoie-le-cas-de-coronavirus-avere-dans-la-region-est-hospitalise-a-annecy|title=Haute-Savoie. Coronavirus : l'\u00e9pouse du patient hospitalis\u00e9 \u00e0 Annecy \u00e9galement infect\u